OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to murdering
OL,4,C'beautiful and caring' Plymouth mother
OL,6,FA man will receive a life sentence
OL,7,Fafter pleading guilty to murdering his
OL,8,Festranged wife who's been described as
OL,9,F'beautiful and caring' mother in
OL,10,FPlymouth.
OL,12,FPaul Antony Butler, 53, admitted
OL,13,Fmurdering Claire Chick, 48, during an
OL,14,Fattack in the city in January.
OL,16,FEmergency services were called to West
OL,17,FHoe Road in the city, where Claire was
OL,18,Ffound seriously injured.
