OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to murdering
OL,4,C'beautiful and caring' Plymouth mother
OL,6,FThe 48-year-old, previously known as
OL,7,FClaire Butler, died in hospital after
OL,8,Fbeing attacked on Wednesday 22 January.
OL,10,FThe university lecturer was taken to
OL,11,Fhospital and died during the early
OL,12,Fhours of Thursday 23 January.
OL,14,FOn Tuesday 18 March, Butler, of
OL,15,FStangray Avenue in Plymouth, Butler,
OL,16,Fof Stangray Avenue, Plymouth, spoke
OL,17,Fonly to confirm his name and enter his
OL,18,Fpleas during the hearing at Plymouth
OL,19,FCrown Court.
