OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to murdering
OL,4,C'beautiful and caring' Plymouth mother
OL,6,FThe defendant, who appeared on video
OL,7,Flink from prison, appeared to wipe a
OL,8,Ftear away from his face as he entered
OL,9,Fhis pleas.
OL,11,FHe also pleaded guilty to a charge of
OL,12,Fpossession of a bladed article.
OL,14,FThe court heard that at the sentencing
OL,15,Fhearing, victim impact statements
OL,16,Fwould be given by Ms Chick's two
OL,17,Fdaughters.
