OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to murdering
OL,4,C'beautiful and caring' Plymouth mother
OL,6,FJudge Robert Linford ordered pre-
OL,7,Fsentence reports and said the
OL,8,Fsentencing hearing would take place on
OL,9,F25 April.
OL,11,FHe told Butler: "I am going to order
OL,12,Fthat a psychiatric report is prepared
OL,13,Fupon you, which will assist the court
OL,14,Fin determining the minimum term that
OL,15,Fmust be served by you before you are
OL,16,Fconsidered for parole.
