OL,6,F"You understand, I know, that the
OL,7,Fsentence for the offence of murder is
OL,8,Ffixed by law and on that date you will
OL,9,Freceive a sentence of life
OL,10,Fimprisonment, but the minimum term
OL,11,Fwill be affected by submissions I hear
OL,12,Ffrom the prosecution barrister and
OL,13,Fyour barrister, and that which is
OL,14,Fcontained in the psychiatric report
OL,15,Fwhich I now order.
OL,17,F"You will remain in custody until that
OL,18,Fday."
