OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to murdering
OL,4,C'beautiful and caring' Plymouth mother
OL,6,FHead of Major Crime Detective
OL,7,FSuperintendent at Devon and Cornwall
OL,8,FPolice, Rachael Bentley, said: "We
OL,9,Fnote the guilty plea entered at
OL,10,FPlymouth Crown Court today by Paul
OL,11,FButler following the murder of Claire
OL,12,FChick in Plymouth on 22 January.
OL,14,F"Our thoughts continue to be with
OL,15,FClaire's family and friends who have
OL,16,Flost someone who was so dearly loved
OL,17,Fand adored by many.
OL,19,F"We will now await and prepare for the
OL,20,Fsentencing of Butler on 25 April by
OL,21,FHis Honour Judge Linford."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
