OL,6,FA vigil was organised by Claire's
OL,7,Ffamily on Monday 3 February where
OL,8,Fcandles were lit and a minute's
OL,9,Fsilence was held at Smeaton's Tower at
OL,10,F6pm.
OL,12,FIn a previous statement released by
OL,13,Fpolice, her family said: "We are
OL,14,Fabsolutely devastated and broken at
OL,15,Fthe loss of our beautiful caring
OL,16,Fmother Claire Chick.
OL,18,F"She was the most beautiful lively
OL,19,Fsoul and was there for everyone.
