OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to murdering
OL,4,C'beautiful and caring' Plymouth mother
OL,6,F"Everyone who knew our mum had so much
OL,7,Fpositive words to say about her. She
OL,8,Fwas the life and soul of any place
OL,9,Fwhere she was.
OL,11,F"She loved to dance and sing, even
OL,12,Fthough she was pretty bad at it; she
OL,13,Fhad no shame in doing it in front of
OL,14,Fany audience.
OL,16,F"We will never get over this as a
OL,17,Ffamily, she was our glue and our go-
OL,18,Fto. We won't ever get the justice our
OL,19,Fmum deserves for this, because no
OL,20,Famount of justiceJwill bring her back.
