OL,6,F"We want to thank everyone for their
OL,7,Fkind words, and we invite anyone who
OL,8,Fknew her to share their memories of
OL,9,Fher.
OL,11,F"We also would like to remind the
OL,12,Fpublic she leaves behind five
OL,13,Fbeautiful grandchildren who all refer
OL,14,Fto her as 'a favourite grandma'.
OL,16,F"We ask you to respect their privacy,
OL,17,Fand everyone remains respectful to
OL,18,Fthem.
